# Define NMAE loss function
def NMAE(observed, pred, nominal):
    absolute_error = np.abs(observed - pred)
    absolute_error /= nominal
    target_idx = np.where(observed >= nominal*0.1)

    return 100 * absolute_error[target_idx].mean()

df = inputs[0]

import pandas as pd
from datetime import datetime

#df['datetime'] = pd.to_datetime(df['datetime'])
dt_start = df['datetime'][0] #시작일정+시간
dt_end = df['datetime'].values[-1] #끝일정+시간

# dt_start부터 dt_end까지 1시간 주기로 날짜데이터 생성
df_allhour = pd.DataFrame(pd.date_range(start=dt_start, end=dt_end, freq='1H'), columns=['datetime'])
df_allhour['datetime'] = df_allhour['datetime'].astype(str)

df_allhour = pd.merge(df_allhour, df, on='datetime', how='outer')
#늘어난 행에 대한 결측치 처리
df_allhour['forecast_time'] = df_allhour['forecast_time'].ffill() #앞 데이터로 대체
df_allhour["temperature"] = df_allhour["temperature"].interpolate() #선형으로 비례해 결측값 보간
df_allhour["humidity"] = df_allhour["humidity"].interpolate()
df_allhour["windspeed"] = df_allhour["windspeed"].interpolate()
df_allhour["winddirection"] = df_allhour["winddirection"].interpolate()

import pandas as pd
import datetime

df = inputs[0]

# 시간 추출하기
df['_datetime'] = pd.to_datetime(df['datetime'])
df['year'] = df['_datetime'].apply(lambda x: x.year)
df['hour'] = df['_datetime'].apply(lambda x: x.hour)
df['month'] = df['_datetime'].apply(lambda x: x.month)
df['day'] = df['_datetime'].apply(lambda x: x.day)
df = df.drop(['_datetime'], axis = 1)

# 18:00 ~ 6:00 0으로 대체
change_zero = df[((df['hour'] >= 18) & (df['hour'] <= 23))
				|((df['hour'] >= 0) & (df['hour'] <= 6))] 
change_zero['target'] = 0


# 데이터 합치기
others = df[~(((df['hour'] >= 18) & (df['hour'] <= 23))
				|((df['hour'] >= 0) & (df['hour'] <= 6)))]

new_df = pd.concat([others, change_zero], axis = 0)
new_df = new_df.sort_values(['year','month','day','hour'], ascending = True)

# 7:00~17:00 target 0인 구간 확인

import numpy as np

# Define NMAE loss function
def NMAE(observed, pred, nominal):
    absolute_error = np.abs(observed - pred)
    absolute_error /= nominal
    target_idx = np.where(observed >= nominal*0.1)

    return 100 * absolute_error[target_idx].mean()

import numpy as np

# Define NMAE loss function
def NMAE(observed, pred, nominal):
    absolute_error = np.abs(observed - pred)
    absolute_error /= nominal
    target_idx = np.where(observed >= nominal*0.1)

    return 100 * absolute_error[target_idx].mean()
  
  
df = inputs[0]

err = NMAE(df['target'].values, df['prediction'].values, 1100)
